---
title: Smokey Crumbed Chicken Subs & Potato Wedges with Cheesy Cucumber & Avocado Salad
description: Say hello to your new favorite handheld feast! Crispy, smokey crumbed chicken snuggles into soft, toasted subs, ready to be devoured. On the side, golden potato wedges bring the crunch, while a cool cucumber and avocado salad keeps it fresh. It’s a flavor-packed combo that’s big on fun and even bigger on taste!
